node.text:
Chocolate Chip Banana Bread. Follow the recipe👇🏻
- Saving 1/2 a banana, In one bowl mash 2 cups of ripe bananas (3-4 bananas) 
- In another bowl combine 1 cup brown sugar, 1/4 cup of room temperature butter and 1 cup of sour cream
- Whisk in 2 eggs into the sugar mixture until it froths up like a mousse 
- Using a fine mesh strainer, add 1 1/2 cups of all purpose flour, 1 1/4 teaspoons of baking powder, and 1 teaspoon of cinnamon to the bowl of the sugar mixture 
- Mix in the mashed bananas and then fold in the chocolate chips
- Line a loaf pan with parchment paper, and add the banana bread batter
- Place some sliced bananas on top of the batter and bake at 350 degrees F for 1 hour and 5 minutes. Let cool for another hour

Pepperoni Pizza Cone. Follow the recipe👇🏻
- Wrap a strip of your favorite pizza dough around a metal cone
- Place the cones open side down on a baking sheet and bake in a 400 degree F oven for 15 minutes
- In the meantime, make the filling by combining 2 cups of shredded mozzarella cheese, 1 cup of pizza sauce, 1/2 cup of chopped pepperoni and a tablespoon of oregano 
-  Release the metal conde from the dough, and stuff the cone with the filling
- Place a sheet of aluminum foil over a loaf pan and place the cones inside
- Bake open side up for another 5 minutes

Cinnamon Roll Ice Cream Cones. Follow the recipe👇🏻
- Unroll a raw cinnamon roll with the filling facing up
- Wrap the dough around a metal cone starting at the pointed end
- Placethe cone on a parchment lined baking sheet and bake at 350 degrees F for 15 minutes
- Take the cone out of the oven and let cool
- Release the metal cone
- Add the frosting to the center and over the top
- Fill with your favorite ice cream!

Mac and Cheese Lava Cake. Follow the recipe👇🏻
- Add 1/4 cup of butter to a saucepan or pot
- When the butter is melted, whisk in 1/4 cup of flour 
- Cook for a few minutes until the flour and butter combine, and then whisk in 2 cups of milk
- Add 1 tablespoon of garlic powder and onion powder and 1 teaspoon of salt
- When the mixture has thickened, turn off the heat and whisk in 2 cups of sharp cheddar cheese
- When the cheese has melted, add 2 cups of cooked macaroni noodles
- Add 1 cup of the mac and cheese to a ramekin or container
- Press down 1/4 cup of velveeta cheese into the center and cover the top in more mac and cheese so the interior is covered
- Refrigerate for 2 hours
- Heat a deep fryer or pot with cooking oil to 375 degrees F
- In one bowl whisk 5 eggs with 1/4 cup of hot sauce and 1/4 cup of water
- In another bowl add 2 cups of all purpose flour and in another bowl 2 cups of bread crumbs
- Release the macaroni cake from the container and cover it in the flour, then the egg wash, then the bread crumbs, and repeat for a double dredge
- Fry the coated macaroni cake for 5 minutes making sure to rotate it
- For an air fryer, add it to the basket, and spray it with cooking oil
- Bake at 400 degrees for 15 minutes rotating halfway through

Mashed Potato Curly Fries. Follow the recipe👇🏻
- Peel and boil 1/2 pound of Yukon gold (or any yellow waxy potatoes) for 15 minutes
- Mashed them in a bowl and combine them with 1/4 cup of corn starch, 2 teaspoons of onion salt, and two teaspoons of garlic powder
- When they are no longer hot, place the potatoes in a ziploc bag and snip the tip
- Squeeze out a spiral shape on a piece of parchment paper
- Heat 2 cups of cooking oil to 375 degrees F
- Add the potato and cook for 2 minutes
- Flip the potato over and cook for another 2 minutes
- Season with salt and enjoy

Whipped Avocado and Ricotta Toast aka AvoCotta Toast with Spicy Honey. Follow the recipe👇🏻
- In a large bowl, combine 1/2 a ripe avocado with 1/2 cup of ricotta cheese
- Season with a teaspoon of salt and pepper and 1 tablespoon of olive oil
- Whip it until it combines and becomes light and fluffy
- Toast two slices of thick cut bread and cover them in the avocado ricotta mixture
- For the hot honey, combine 1/4 cup of honey with 2 tablespoons of your favorite hot sauce
- Add the hot honey, sprinkle on some smoked paprika dn season with course salt

Fried Beef Salami and Beef Bologna Sandwich. Follow the recipe👇🏻
- Fry some beef salami and beef bologna on a medium frying pan until they are lightly cooked.
- Make a small incision to help them cook flat 
- Spread some yellow mustard on an onion roll and layer it with a slice of swiss, a slice of salami, bologna, another slice of salami and bologna making sure to interchange the meat, and another slice of swiss
- Use a panini press or sandwich press to fry the sandwich on both sides for about 3 minutes
- Slice in half and enjoy
